PIPR_Description:
PlayyOn provides everything needed to manage one’s sports life, all in one place.
•	User controlled sports profile that higlights historical and current participation;
•	Visual showcase for achievements and participation;
•	News feed from teams, groups and people that are part of one’s sports life;
•	Calendar events with RSVP functionality;
•	Team pages for announcements and photo sharing;

PlayyOn provides athletes with a free, sports centric platform that highlights their lifelong participation and achievements. Powered by participants, PlayyOn emphasizes content as a source for collaboration and inspiration.

People do not obtain the knowledge they want – taking online courses! 
Only 4% of online students stay long enough to complete the courses because of short attention span, lack of time and motivation. 

Coursmos.com is the world`s first micro learning platform.
Our product - addresses the Teaching and Learning area and offers the following benefits to both teachers and students:

•	Fits into a student’s attention span and technological habits;
•	Delivers knowledge in concise way on a device that is ubiquitous ~ the smartphone or tablet;
•	Course creation is easy and fast to move from development to publishing a course;
•	The micro courses are effective - not only in general learning, but also in reinforcing topical lessons previously learned;
•	Interconnected or clustering of a series of micro-courses allows the student to surf through the knowledge database in any direction.
